er On Serial Killers, Lead Poisoning, and Other Midcentury Disasters</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">June 13, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/molly-odintz/">Molly Odintz</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/the-horror-of-a-border-laura-elliott-on-writing-the-abject/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/06/horror-feat-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/the-horror-of-a-border-laura-elliott-on-writing-the-abject/">The Horror of a Border: Laura Elliott On Writing the Abject</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">June 13, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/lauraelliott/">Laura Ellliott</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/everythings-coming-up-cozies/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2019/10/england-village-feat-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/everythings-coming-up-cozies/">Everything’s Coming Up Cozies</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">June 13, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/karendukess/">Karen Dukess</a></span></div></li></ul></li>
